'''''DS''''' was the designation given to a group of two [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. They participated in the [[Diplomatic Summit at Sullust|diplomatic meeting]] between the [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustans]] and the Alliance to Restore the Republic near [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]] during [[Operation Strike Fear]], carrying part of the Alliance delegation. The meeting was interrupted by the arrival of the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Invincible (Strike Fear)|''Invincible'']]. [[Hamo Blastwell]] and [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]], flying [[R-22 Spearhead starfighter|R-22 Spearheads]], held off the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[TIE series/Legends|fighters]] until the meeting was concluded and all ships fled into [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]].

